### Responsive design

```ts
// Mobile-first approach
<div className="px-4 py-8 md:px-6 md:py-12 lg:px-8 lg:py-16">
  {/* Espacement progressif */}
</div>

// Grille responsive
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
  {/* Items */}
</div>

